And finally, the Rational Decision Maker can take the wheel and I can start working on the presentation.
The Panic Monster explains much of the rather foolish behavior of the procrastinator, like how someone like me can spend two weeks unable to start a sentence of a dissertation and miraculously find the incredible work ethic to stay awake all night to write 8 pages.
All this situation, with these three characters, is the procrastinator's system.
It's not pretty, but in the end, it works.
